channel.title: Private server problems
channel.description: When i first got my computer, i was able to use the silabs webclient until one day when i restarted my computer. i got back on and i went to the webclient but it said that the cache could not be downloaded. then when i tried to use the mopar webclient, the client opens for 5 seconds and then the window closes itself. Then i downloaded another client that ive used before and this one works except that i cant get on ANY server weather its on or offline. ill type in the correct IP address and port but when i click log-in, it says "error connecting to server". then the next times i try to get on, it doesnt even attempt to connect and still says error connecting to server. it also does this with all my downloadble clients. The only private server i was ever able to connect to was dodian on their own webclient. Any help?
